south korea to resist currenc revalu south korean financ minist chung in-yong will resist pressur for a currenc revalu to cut south korea 's trade surplu with the unit state when he meet treasuri secretari jame baker next week , financ ministri offici said . they said chung would leav monday to attend the intern monetari fund 's interim committe meet and to hold talk with baker and other u.s. offici on way to reduc the surplu . the april 9 committe meet is expect to review the agreement by six industri nation in pari last month that newly-industri countri , such as south korea and taiwan , should allow their currenc to increas in valu .